# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# Audit log review requires ADMIN and an authenticated session.
# Auth errors use the localized ProblemDetail shape with title/status/detail/messageKey/message/language.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here

### AuditLogController - list audit logs (ADMIN + authenticated session)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?page=0&size=20&sort=id,desc
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/json

### AuditLogController - filter audit logs by target type, action, and actor login
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?targetType=AUTHENTICATION&action=LOGIN_SUCCESS&actorLogin=admin-user
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/json

### AuditLogController - list audit logs without authentication (401 localized ProblemDetail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs
Accept: application/problem+json

### AuditLogController - list audit logs as non-admin user (403 localized ProblemDetail)
# Replace the session cookie with a regular authenticated USER session.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/problem+json
